Package: fastbioclim
Type: Package
Title: Scalable and Flexible Derivation of Custom-Time Bioclimatic and Environmental Summary Variables
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: c(person("Gonzalo E.", "Pinilla-Buitrago", 
